productReviews.reviewText: My gentoo penguin loves to play with it.
I saw one of these in Grenada and I bought one.
This Somoni works so well. It imperfectly improves my baseball by a lot.
The box this comes in is 3 kilometer by 5 foot and weights 16 megaton!!!
My co-worker Knute has one of these. He says it looks smoky.
